# ===================================================================
#                    KYTHIA BOT CONFIGURATION
# ===================================================================
#
# 📋 SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
#
#   1. Copy this file and rename it to '.env'
#   2. Start with the "QUICK START" section below - fill ONLY those fields
#   3. Test your bot! If it works, you're done with basic setup
#   4. (Optional) Configure additional features in the sections below
#
# ⚠️  SECURITY WARNING:
#   - NEVER commit the .env file to version control!
#   - NEVER share your tokens or secrets publicly!
#   - Keep this file confidential and secure!
#
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# ⚠️  IMPORTANT - READ THIS BEFORE ASKING FOR HELP ⚠️
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#
#   🚫 BASIC SETUP SUPPORT POLICY:
#
#   Questions like "How do I get a Discord token?" or "Where do I put
#   the .env file?" WILL NOT BE ANSWERED by the developer.
#
#   ALL SETUP INSTRUCTIONS ARE ALREADY IN THIS FILE AND THE README.
#
#   👉 RTFM (Read The F*cking Manual) 👈
#
#   If you cannot follow the clear instructions provided here,
#   this bot is not for you. No exceptions.
#
#   Advanced technical questions are welcome in Discord.
#   Basic setup questions will be ignored.
#
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#
# 🆘 RESOURCES:
#   - Discord Server (Advanced Support Only): https://dsc.gg/kythia
#   - Documentation: https://kythia.me
#   - README.md: Read it thoroughly before asking anything
